del 🚀\nToken Airdrop\nNFT Pets (future)\n\n🧠 7. Psychology Strategy (Why Users Stay)\n🐾 Emotional attachment\n🎯 Daily tasks\n🏆 Competition\n🎁 Rewards\n📈 Progress\n👉 This is why games like Pou became viral\n\n🛠️ 8. Tech Stack (Telegram Bot)\nBackend:\nNode.js / Python (FastAPI)\nDatabase:\nMongoDB / PostgreSQL\nTelegram:\nBot API + Web Apps\nBlockchain (Optional):\nERC-20 Token\nWallet integration\n\n🔄 9. 20-Day Build Roadmap\n🗓️ Week 1:\nBot setup\nPet system basic\nFeed + XP system\n🗓️ Week 2:\nMini games\nCoin system\nShop\n🗓️ Week 3:\nLeaderboard\nInvite system\nUI improvement\n🗓️ Week 4:\nAirdrop logic\nScaling + testing\nLaunch 🚀\n\n🚀 10. Growth Strategy\nReferral system 🔥\nDaily rewards\nLimited-time events\nInfluencer promotion\n\n🎯 Final Summary\n👉 This game is powerful because:\nEasy to build\nHighly addictive\nScalable\nWeb3-ready\n👉 If executed well, it can become:\nNext Hamster Kombat-type viral game\n	admin	2026-04-30 13:09:36.091605	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd
