4a09790e-f020-4d43-a680-0d8b21c9e47a	Mine-A-Meme (Telegram Bot Game)	🎮 Mine-A-Meme (Telegram Bot Game)\n🧠 Core Concept\nPlayers act as meme miners digging daily “viral layers” to discover trending meme tokens (fake or real-inspired like DOGE-style).\n⛏ Tap / Click to mine\n💰 Earn Meme Coins\n📈 Upgrade mining rigs\n🔥 Discover “Trending Meme Tokens of the Week”\n🏆 Compete on leaderboard\n\n⚙️ Game Loop (Very Important)\nThis is what keeps users addicted:\nOpen bot\nTap “Mine” → earn coins\nDiscover meme token (random drop)\nUpgrade tools\nInvite friends → boost mining\nDaily reset → new meme trends\nWeekly jackpot / winner\n👉 Simple, repeatable, addictive.\n\n🧩 Core Modules\n1. 👤 User System\nTelegram ID login\nWallet (coins, tokens)\nEnergy system (limits tapping)\n\n2. ⛏ Mining System\nTap button OR auto-miner\nEnergy decreases per tap\nRecharge over time\nAdvanced twist:\nRare “Golden Meme Block” → big reward\n“Rug Pull Trap” → lose some coins 😄\n\n3. 🪙 Meme Token System\nEvery week:\n3–5 trending meme tokens generated:\ne.g. DogeX, PepeGold, CatCoin\nEach token has:\nRarity (Common → Legendary)\nPrice multiplier\n👉 Inspired by real meme hype cycles.\n\n4. 📈 Upgrade System\nPlayers can upgrade:\nMining speed\nEnergy capacity\nLuck (better meme drops)\n\n5. 👫 Referral System (Growth Engine)\nInvite = +20% mining boost\nMulti-level bonus\nLeaderboard rewards\n👉 This is how games like Notcoin exploded.\n\n6. 🎁 Daily & Weekly Rewards\nDaily login bonus\nWeekly jackpot pool:\nTop miners win rewards\n\n7. 🏆 Leaderboard\nTop miners of the week\nTop referrals\nTop rare token holders\n\n8. 💸 Future Airdrop (Optional)\nIf you launch token later:\nConvert in-game coins → real tokens\nLike Hamster Kombat model\n\n🔄 Gameplay Flow (User Journey)\nStart Bot\n  ↓\nGet Starter Pickaxe\n  ↓\nTap Mine ⛏\n  ↓\nFind Meme Tokens 🪙\n  ↓\nUpgrade Tools ⚙️\n  ↓\nInvite Friends 👥\n  ↓\nEarn More Faster 🚀\n  ↓\nWeekly Rewards 🏆\n\n🧠 Smart Features (Make it Viral)\n🔥 Trending System\nAdmin panel updates weekly tokens\nOR auto-fetch from Twitter trends\n\n🎰 Random Events\n“Meme Explosion” → 5x rewards (10 mins)\n“Server Crash” → funny penalty event\n\n😂 Meme Integration\nShow meme images when mining\nAdd humor = higher retention\n\n🛠 Tech Stack (Simple + Fast)\nBackend:\nNode.js (Telegraf.js)\nMongoDB / Firebase\nBot:\nTelegram Bot API\nOptional:\nWebApp UI (React)\n\n📅 20-Day Development Plan\nWeek 1:\nBot setup\nMining system\nUser wallet\nWeek 2:\nUpgrades\nReferral system\nLeaderboard\nWeek 3:\nMeme token system\nEvents + rewards\nUI polish\n\n💡 Monetization\nTelegram Stars ⭐\nPremium upgrades\nEnergy refill\nNFT tools (future)\n\n⚠️ Reality Check\nAvoid:\nReal money gambling (legal risk in India)\nFake “guaranteed crypto earnings”\nInstead:\n 👉 Start as fun + points-based game, then add token later.\n\n🚀 Next Level Idea (Very Powerful)\nCombine with your lottery idea:\n👉 Mining coins = lottery tickets\n 👉 Weekly meme jackpot winner\n\n🎯 Final Verdict\nThis idea can work VERY WELL if you focus on:\nViral loop (referrals)\nSimple gameplay\nWeekly excitement\n	admin	2026-05-01 03:17:14.235098	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd
66078e97-8634-4bac-9fc9-4206dd13d3c6	Lottery Projects(Telegram bot game)	1.Lottery Projects:🎮 SCAI Lucky Loop.\n1. Product Overview\nGame Type: Free-to-Play Daily Lottery\n Platform: Telegram Bot + Web3 Integration\n Core Idea:\n Users earn coins for free, use them to buy lottery tickets, and win rewards. Once they reach a threshold, they can withdraw blockchain tokens — but only after completing referral conditions (viral growth system).\n\n🎮 2. Core Gameplay Loop\nStep-by-Step Flow:\nUser joins Telegram bot\nUser earns free coins (via spin or tasks)\nUser buys lottery tickets using coins\nDaily lottery draw selects a winner\nWinner receives coin reward\nUser accumulates coins\nAt 1000 coins → withdraw unlocked (after referrals)\n\n🎟️ 3. Ticket System\nRules:\nTotal tickets per day: 50\nMax per user: 2 tickets\nTicket price: 10 coins\nBehavior:\nWhen a user buys a ticket:\n10 coins are deducted\nTicket is reserved\nReserved ticket cannot be purchased again\nOnly available tickets are shown to users\n\n⏰ 4. Daily Timing System\nTime\nAction\n09:00 – 15:00\nTicket purchase open\nAfter 15:00\nSales closed\n18:00\nWinner declared\n\n\n🎲 5. Winner Selection System\nBasic Logic:\nAll sold tickets are collected\nOne random ticket is selected\nThat ticket’s owner is the winner\nExample:\nconst winner = tickets[Math.floor(Math.random() * tickets.length)];\n👉 Future improvement:\nBlockchain-based randomness (fair & transparent)\n\n💰 6. Economy Design (Very Important)\nCurrent Issue:\nTotal collected: 50 × 10 = 500 coins\nReward: 200 coins\n\n✅ Recommended Economy:\nWinner reward: 100 coins\nPlatform fee: 100 coins\nBurn/Reserve: remaining\n👉 This ensures:\nUser motivation\nLong-term sustainability\n\n🪙 7. Coin System\nTypes:\nCoins (Off-chain):\nStored in database\nUsed for gameplay\nSCAI Tokens (On-chain):\nReal blockchain asset\nWithdrawable\n\n🔐 8. Withdrawal System (Viral Lock Mechanism)\nThis is your growth engine 🚀\n\n🎯 Goal:\n1000 coins = 10 SCAI tokens\n\n✅ Conditions:\nUser must have ≥ 1000 coins\nUser must refer 5 active users\n\n🔒 If Locked:\n"Withdraw locked! Invite 5 friends to unlock your reward."\n\n🔓 Unlock Flow:\nUser completes 5 referrals\nWithdraw button becomes active\nUser enters wallet address\nTokens are sent\n\n🔗 9. Blockchain Integration\nToken Standard:\nERC-20 token using Solidity\n\nFlow:\nBackend verifies withdrawal request\nBackend calls smart contract\nTokens transferred to user wallet\n\nSmart Contract Function:\nfunction transfer(address to, uint amount) public {\n   require(balance[msg.sender] >= amount);\n   balance[msg.sender] -= amount;\n   balance[to] += amount;\n}\n\n⚙️ 10. System Architecture\nTelegram Bot (Frontend)\n       ↓\nNode.js Backend (Logic)\n       ↓\nDatabase (Users, Tickets, Coins)\n       ↓\nBlockchain (Token Transfer)\n\n🗄️ 11. Database Design\nUsers Table:\nid\ncoins\nreferral_count\nwallet_address\n\nTickets Table:\nid\nuser_id\ndate\n\nWithdrawals Table:\nid\nuser_id\namount\nstatus\n\n⚠️ 12. Risk Management\n❌ Fake Referrals\n✔ Solution:\nCount only users who:\nStart bot\nPlay game\n\n❌ Multiple Accounts\n✔ Solution:\nTrack Telegram ID + IP/device\n\n❌ Coin Abuse\n✔ Solution:\nDaily earning limits\n\n💡 13. Growth Features\nReferral bonus (e.g., 50 coins)\nDaily spin rewards\nWeekly jackpot event\nLeaderboard rankings\n\n🧑‍💼 14. Admin System\nAdmin Panel Features:\nView users\nView ticket sales\nManage withdrawals\nSend tokens manually (optional)\n\nTwo Options:\nManual approval (admin clicks send)\nAutomatic withdrawal (recommended)\n\n🚀 15. Complete User Journey\nUser joins bot\nEarns free coins\nBuys tickets daily\nWins or loses\nInvites friends\nReaches 1000 coins\nUnlocks withdrawal\nReceives SCAI tokens \n\n\n—--------->How to work?\n->here use https://chatgpt.com/ or other AI tools	admin	2026-05-01 03:20:13.020166	\N	https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd
