15d1f6aa-8678-46e7-af30-57f861a5f3b4	SCAI Glass Survival(Telegram bot game)	🌉 Game Concept: SCAI Glass Survival\nInspired by the Squid Game, this Telegram-based game creates a high-risk, high-reward survival experience.\nPlayers must cross a bridge made of glass panels. Each step has:\nOne Safe (strong) glass\nOne Broken (weak) glass\nChoose wrong → you fall → game over ❌\n Choose right → move forward ✅\n\n🎮 1. Gameplay (How It Works)\n🔹 Basic Structure\nTotal Steps: 10\nEach step has 2 choices:\nLeft (L)\nRight (R)\n🔹 Entry Cost\n1 Ticket = 10 Coins\nCoins are earned from your Lottery / Lucky Spin system\n🔹 Winning Condition\nPlayer must correctly choose all 10 steps\nExample path:\n\n L → R → R → L → L → R → R → L → R → L\n\n\n🔹 Rewards\n🎁 500 Coins OR\n💰 2 SCAI Tokens (auto transfer to wallet)\n\n⚙️ 2. Game Logic & Flow\n🔹 Daily Rounds\n5 rounds per day:\n10:00 AM\n1:00 PM\n4:00 PM\n7:00 PM\n10:00 PM\n🔹 Limited Players\nMax 50 players per round\n🔹 Elimination Rule\nWrong step → Instant elimination\nPlayer must:\nWait for next round OR\nPay 10 coins again\n🔹 Session Flow\nUser joins round\nTicket deducted\nGame starts\nStep-by-step selection\nEither:\n❌ Eliminated\n🏆 Wins reward\n\n🧠 3. Full Game Scenario (User Journey)\n👤 Step 1: User Entry\nUser opens Telegram bot\nClicks “Play Glass Survival”\nPays 10 coins\n\n🎯 Step 2: Round Start\nCountdown starts (e.g. 10 seconds)\nAll 50 players enter together\n\n🌉 Step 3: Gameplay\nFor each step:\nUI shows 2 glass panels\nUser clicks Left or Right\nSystem checks:\nIf correct → move forward\nIf wrong → animation → fall → eliminated\n\n🎬 Step 4: Visual Feedback\nSafe step → smooth walk animation\nWrong step → glass break animation 💥\n\n🏁 Step 5: End Result\nIf user reaches Step 10:\n🎉 Winner screen\nCoins/SCAI credited\nIf eliminated:\n❌ “You fell at Step 6”\nShow retry option\n\n🛠️ 4. 20-Day Development Plan\n📅 Days 1–5: Backend\nGenerate random safe path:\n\n Example: [L, R, R, L, L, R, ...]\n\n\nStore per round\nSave user progress (step number)\n\n📅 Days 6–12: Frontend (React)\nBuild 2D / 3D bridge UI\nAdd:\nClick interaction\nStep progression\nAnimations\n👉 Use:\nFramer Motion (for animations)\nSound effects (optional)\n\n📅 Days 13–16: Blockchain Integration\nConnect wallet\nOn win:\nTrigger smart contract\nTransfer SCAI tokens\n\n📅 Days 17–20: Viral Features\nAdd Referral Condition\nWithdraw only after 5 referrals\nAdd:\nLeaderboard\nShare results button\n“Watch others play” mode (optional)\n\n🚀 5. Why This Game Will Go Viral\n🔥 High Risk = High Excitement\nPlayers lose instantly → addictive retry loop\n💸 High Reward\n10 coins → 500 coins reward\nHuge psychological pull\n👥 Social Competition\nPlayers compare:\n“I reached Step 8”\n“You failed at Step 3”\n🔗 SCAI Ecosystem Growth\nCoins → SCAI conversion\nDrives token demand\n\n💡 6. Technical Tips (Important)\n🧩 State Management\nSave:\nCurrent step\nSelected path\nSo refresh doesn’t reset progress\n	in-progress	2026-04-29 00:00:00	2027-11-23 00:00:00	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	2026-04-29 13:28:24.7	2026-04-29 13:28:24.7	\N	Interns Project	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd	a9c5da89-3090-4c4d-9039-6a0174486660
b63c34cb-4134-4309-8d27-0b4a583abc52	SCAI Tap Empire(Telegram bot game)	💡 1. Core Idea (Simple but Powerful)\nSCAI Tap Empire is a Telegram-based mini game where users:\n👉 Tap → Earn coins\n👉 Upgrade → Increase earnings\n👉 Invite → Multiply income\n👉 Compete → Win rewards\nBut the real hook is:\n🔥 “Your coins may convert into future rewards / tokens”\n(similar growth model used by Notcoin)\n\n🔁 2. Full Gameplay System (Loop Design)\n🧩 Main Loop\nUser opens bot\nClicks Play\nTap button appears\nTap → coins increase\nEnergy reduces\nUse coins → buy upgrades\nCome back after refill\n👉 This loop = addiction + retention\n\n⚙️ 3. Deep Feature Breakdown\n👆 A. Tap Engine (Core System)\nBase Rules:\n1 Tap = 1 coin\nMax 5 taps/sec (anti-cheat)\nEnhancements:\nTap animation (coin burst 💥)\nHaptic/vibration (mobile)\nCombo system (fast taps = bonus)\n\n⚡ B. Energy System (Anti-Abuse + Retention)\nParameter\nValue\nMax Energy\n100\nCost per Tap\n1\nRegen Speed\n1 energy / 30 sec\n\nUpgrades:\nMax Energy ↑ (100 → 500)\nRegen Speed ↑ (30s → 10s)\n👉 Without this = bots will destroy your game\n\n⬆️ C. Upgrade System (Progression Engine)\nUpgrade Types:\nTap Power\n+1 coin per tap\nCost increases exponentially\nAuto Tap (Idle Income)\nEarn coins without tapping\nExample: 20 coins/min\nEnergy Boost\nIncrease max energy\nTurbo Boost\n2x coins for 10 minutes\n\n🤖 D. Idle Income System\nEven when user is offline:\nEarn coins passively\nCap: 3–6 hours max\n👉 Forces users to return\n\n🎁 E. Reward Systems\nDaily Login\nDay 1 → 100 coins\nDay 7 → 1000 coins\nMissions\nTap 1000 times\nInvite 2 friends\nUpgrade level 5\n\n👥 F. Referral System (Growth Engine)\nMechanics:\nInvite user → +500 coins\nWhen friend earns → you earn %\n👉 This is what makes games viral\n\n🏆 G. Leaderboard\nTop coin holders\nWeekly reset\nRewards:\nRank 1 → Big bonus\nRank 2–10 → medium reward\n\n💰 4. Economy Design (Critical Part)\n🪙 Currency Flow\nTap → Earn → Upgrade → Earn Faster → Repeat\n⚠️ Control System\nIncrease upgrade cost\nLimit daily rewards\nCap idle earnings\n\n🎯 Reward Vision\nFuture options:\nToken airdrop (like Notcoin)\nGift cards\nPremium upgrades\n\n🧠 5. Engagement Strategy\nTo keep users active:\nDaily streak system\nLimited-time events\n“2x Tap Hour”\nLucky bonus taps 🎰\n\n🛠️ 6. Technical Architecture\nBackend\nNode.js\nTelegraf\nFrontend\nTelegram WebApp (HTML + JS)\nDatabase\nMongoDB\n\n📊 7. Database Structure\nUsers\nuser_id\ncoins\nenergy\ntap_power\nreferrals\nlast_active\nUpgrades\nuser_id\ntype\nlevel\nLogs\ntap_count\nrewards\n\n🚀 8. 20-Day Execution Plan\n🗓️ Days 1–5\nBot setup\nDB setup\nBasic UI\n🗓️ Days 6–10\nTap + Energy system\n🗓️ Days 11–15\nUpgrade + rewards\n🗓️ Days 16–18\nReferral + leaderboard\n🗓️ Days 19–20\nTesting + launch\n\n🔥 9. Advanced Add-ons (After Launch)\n🎡 Spin wheel\n💎 Premium system\n🐾 Pet system\n🎯 Mini-games\n\n⚠️ 10. Reality Check (Important)\nIf you want success:\nGame must feel rewarding in first 5 minutes\nReferral system must be strong\nUI must be smooth (no lag)\nPromise future value (token/reward)\n\n🧩 Final Simple Summary\n👉 Easy to build\n👉 Easy to scale\n👉 High viral potential\nFormula:\nTap + Reward + Referral + Future Promise = Growth 🚀\n	in-progress	2026-04-29 00:00:00	2027-06-22 00:00:00	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	2026-04-29 13:29:32.251	2026-04-29 13:29:32.251	\N	Interns Project	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd	a9c5da89-3090-4c4d-9039-6a0174486660
