Safe:\n   Add Reward\n   Increase Score\nELSE:\n   End Game\n   Save Score\n\n🗂️ 5. Project Structure (Clean Setup)\nlumberjack-game/\n│\n├── bot/\n│   ├── handlers/\n│   ├── commands/\n│   └── keyboards/\n│\n├── backend/\n│   ├── controllers/\n│   ├── services/\n│   ├── models/\n│   └── routes/\n│\n├── game-engine/\n│   ├── logic.js\n│   ├── rewards.js\n│   └── energy.js\n│\n├── database/\n│   └── schema.sql\n│\n└── frontend (optional WebApp)\n\n💻 6. Recommended Tech Stack (Best Choice)\n🔹 Option A (Fastest - Beginner Friendly)\nBackend: Node.js (Express)\nBot: Telegraf.js\nDatabase: MongoDB\n\n🔹 Option B (More Scalable)\nBackend: Node.js + NestJS\nDatabase: PostgreSQL\nCache: Redis\n\n🔹 Option C (Simple + Cheap)\nBackend: Python (FastAPI)\nBot: Aiogram\n\n🧠 7. Game Logic Example (Simplified)\nfunction chopTree(user) {\n   if (user.energy <= 0) return "No energy";\n\n   user.energy--;\n\n   let branch = Math.random() < 0.3; // 30% chance\n\n   if (branch) {\n       return "Game Over";\n   } else {\n       user.coins += 10;\n       user.wood += 5;\n       return "Success";\n   }\n}\n\n📅 8. 20-Day Development Plan\n🗓️ Week 1 (Core Build)\nBot setup\nUser system\nBasic gameplay logic\n\n🗓️ Week 2 (Game Features)\nEnergy system\nRewards\nUpgrades\n\n🗓️ Week 3 (Growth Features)\nLeaderboard\nReferral system\nUI improvements\n\n🗓️ Final Days\nTesting\nBug fixing\nLaunch 🚀\n\n💰 9. Monetization Ideas\nTelegram Stars ⭐\nBoost packs\nPremium axe skins\nAds (optional)\nFuture token\n\n🚀 10. Advanced Features (Later)\nBoss trees 🌳\nMultiplayer battle\nClan system\nNFT tools (Web3 upgrade)\n\n🧩 Final Insight\nThis game works because:\nSimple tap mechanic\nAddictive loop\nViral (referrals)\nExpandable to crypto\n	in-progress	2026-04-29 00:00:00	2027-10-27 00:00:00	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	2026-04-29 13:30:24.956	2026-04-29 13:30:24.956	\N	Interns Project	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd	a9c5da89-3090