05ebafea-c796-4155-b3a0-9ec76bf94a39	Mine-A-Meme (Telegram Bot Game)	🎮 Mine-A-Meme (Telegram Bot Game)\n🧠 Core Concept\nPlayers act as meme miners digging daily “viral layers” to discover trending meme tokens (fake or real-inspired like DOGE-style).\n⛏ Tap / Click to mine\n💰 Earn Meme Coins\n📈 Upgrade mining rigs\n🔥 Discover “Trending Meme Tokens of the Week”\n🏆 Compete on leaderboard\n\n⚙️ Game Loop (Very Important)\nThis is what keeps users addicted:\nOpen bot\nTap “Mine” → earn coins\nDiscover meme token (random drop)\nUpgrade tools\nInvite friends → boost mining\nDaily reset → new meme trends\nWeekly jackpot / winner\n👉 Simple, repeatable, addictive.\n\n🧩 Core Modules\n1. 👤 User System\nTelegram ID login\nWallet (coins, tokens)\nEnergy system (limits tapping)\n\n2. ⛏ Mining System\nTap button OR auto-miner\nEnergy decreases per tap\nRecharge over time\nAdvanced twist:\nRare “Golden Meme Block” → big reward\n“Rug Pull Trap” → lose some coins 😄\n\n3. 🪙 Meme Token System\nEvery week:\n3–5 trending meme tokens generated:\ne.g. DogeX, PepeGold, CatCoin\nEach token has:\nRarity (Common → Legendary)\nPrice multiplier\n👉 Inspired by real meme hype cycles.\n\n4. 📈 Upgrade System\nPlayers can upgrade:\nMining speed\nEnergy capacity\nLuck (better meme drops)\n\n5. 👫 Referral System (Growth Engine)\nInvite = +20% mining boost\nMulti-level bonus\nLeaderboard rewards\n👉 This is how games like Notcoin exploded.\n\n6. 🎁 Daily & Weekly Rewards\nDaily login bonus\nWeekly jackpot pool:\nTop miners win rewards\n\n7. 🏆 Leaderboard\nTop miners of the week\nTop referrals\nTop rare token holders\n\n8. 💸 Future Airdrop (Optional)\nIf you launch token later:\nConvert in-game coins → real tokens\nLike Hamster Kombat model\n\n🔄 Gameplay Flow (User Journey)\nStart Bot\n  ↓\nGet Starter Pickaxe\n  ↓\nTap Mine ⛏\n  ↓\nFind Meme Tokens 🪙\n  ↓\nUpgrade Tools ⚙️\n  ↓\nInvite Friends 👥\n  ↓\nEarn More Faster 🚀\n  ↓\nWeekly Rewards 🏆\n\n🧠 Smart Features (Make it Viral)\n🔥 Trending System\nAdmin panel updates weekly tokens\nOR auto-fetch from Twitter trends\n\n🎰 Random Events\n“Meme Explosion” → 5x rewards (10 mins)\n“Server Crash” → funny penalty event\n\n😂 Meme Integration\nShow meme images when mining\nAdd humor = higher retention\n\n🛠 Tech Stack (Simple + Fast)\nBackend:\nNode.js (Telegraf.js)\nMongoDB / Firebase\nBot:\nTelegram Bot API\nOptional:\nWebApp UI (React)\n\n📅 20-Day Development Plan\nWeek 1:\nBot setup\nMining system\nUser wallet\nWeek 2:\nUpgrades\nReferral system\nLeaderboard\nWeek 3:\nMeme token system\nEvents + rewards\nUI polish\n\n💡 Monetization\nTelegram Stars ⭐\nPremium upgrades\nEnergy refill\nNFT tools (future)\n\n⚠️ Reality Check\nAvoid:\nReal money gambling (legal risk in India)\nFake “guaranteed crypto earnings”\nInstead:\n 👉 Start as fun + points-based game, then add token later.\n\n🚀 Next Level Idea (Very Powerful)\nCombine with your lottery idea:\n👉 Mining coins = lottery tickets\n 👉 Weekly meme jackpot winner\n\n🎯 Final Verdict\nThis idea can work VERY WELL if you focus on:\nViral loop (referrals)\nSimple gameplay\nWeekly excitement\n	in-progress	2026-04-29 00:00:00	2027-10-28 00:00:00	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	2026-04-29 13:31:24.842	2026-04-29 13:31:24.842	\N	Interns Project	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd	a9c5da89-3090-4c4d-9039-6a0174486660
28e9f47b-5890-4b13-b4ed-a910f779781b	Virtual Pet Game (Telegram Bot)	🎮 1. Game Concept\nGame Name Ideas:\nPetVerse 🐾\nSCAI Pet Life\nMetaPet World\n👉 Users get a virtual pet inside a Telegram bot.\nThey must feed, play, train, and evolve their pet daily.\n💡 Core Psychology:\nOwnership (My Pet 🐶)\nProgress (Level Up 🚀)\nReward (Coins + Airdrop 💰)\nSocial (Show-off + Battles 🏆)\n\n🔁 2. Core Gameplay Loop (Daily Hook)\nEvery user repeats this loop daily:\n🥗 Feed Pet → Gain XP\n🎾 Play Game → Earn Coins\n💤 Rest → Faster Recovery\n🧠 Train → Unlock Skills\n📈 Level Up → New Features\n👉 This creates addiction loop like Tamagotchi + modern Web3 games\n\n🧩 3. Game Modules (System Design)\n🔹 A. Pet System\nPet Types: Dog 🐶, Cat 🐱, Dragon 🐉 (unlock later)\nStats:\nHunger 🍗\nHappiness 😊\nEnergy ⚡\nLevel 📊\n👉 If ignored:\nPet becomes sad 😢\nRewards decrease\n\n🔹 B. Mini Games Module\nSimple Telegram-based games:\nTap Game (earn coins)\nMemory Game 🧠\nQuiz Game ❓\n💰 Reward:\nCoins + XP\n\n🔹 C. Economy System\nCurrency Types:\n🪙 Coins (earn in-game)\n💎 Gems (premium / rare)\nUsage:\nBuy food 🍔\nBuy toys 🎾\nBuy skins 👕\nUpgrade pet 🚀\n\n🔹 D. Shop System\nFood Packs\nToys\nAccessories\nBoosters\n💡 Monetization ready module\n\n🔹 E. Social System\n👥 Invite Friends → Earn rewards\n🏆 Leaderboard\n⚔️ Pet Battles (future update)\n\n🔹 F. Airdrop / Token System (IMPORTANT 🚀)\n👉 Same model like:\nNotcoin\nHamster Kombat\nConcept:\nPoints = Future Tokens\nEarly users = Big reward\n\n📊 4. Progression System\nLevel\nUnlock Feature\n1\nBasic Pet\n5\nMini Games\n10\nAccessories\n15\nSocial Features\n20\nPet Evolution 🐉\n30\nPvP Battles\n\n\n🧬 5. Pet Evolution System (HOOK 🔥)\n\n\n\n6\n👉 Pet changes form based on:\nLevel\nActivity\nItems used\nExample:\nDog 🐶 → Super Dog 🐕‍🦺 → Fire Beast 🔥\n💡 This keeps users engaged for weeks/months\n\n💸 6. Monetization Strategy\nFree Model (Viral Growth)\nDaily rewards\nInvite bonus\nAd-based rewards\nPaid Model 💰\nBuy Gems\nPremium Pet Skins\nBoost Packs\nWeb3 Model 🚀\nToken Airdrop\nNFT Pets (future)\n\n🧠 7. Psychology Strategy (Why Users Stay)\n🐾 Emotional attachment\n🎯 Daily tasks\n🏆 Competition\n🎁 Rewards\n📈 Progress\n👉 This is why games like Pou became viral\n\n🛠️ 8. Tech Stack (Telegram Bot)\nBackend:\nNode.js / Python (FastAPI)\nDatabase:\nMongoDB / PostgreSQL\nTelegram:\nBot API + Web Apps\nBlockchain (Optional):\nERC-20 Token\nWallet integration\n\n🔄 9. 20-Day Build Roadmap\n🗓️ Week 1:\nBot setup\nPet system basic\nFeed + XP system\n🗓️ Week 2:\nMini games\nCoin system\nShop\n🗓️ Week 3:\nLeaderboard\nInvite system\nUI improvement\n🗓️ Week 4:\nAirdrop logic\nScaling + testing\nLaunch 🚀\n\n🚀 10. Growth Strategy\nReferral system 🔥\nDaily rewards\nLimited-time events\nInfluencer promotion\n\n🎯 Final Summary\n👉 This game is powerful because:\nEasy to build\nHighly addictive\nScalable\nWeb3-ready\n👉 If executed well, it can become:\nNext Hamster Kombat-type viral game\n	in-progress	2026-04-29 00:00:00	2028-06-13 00:00:00	\N	 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	2026-04-29 13:32:23.912	2026-04-29 13:32:23.912	\N	Interns Project	f90cf240-9aa2-4c48-813f-b9b6a1ff4ddd	a9c5da89-3090-4c4d-9039-6a0174486660
