eply scripts\n ✔ 1–3 interested leads (target)\n\n📅 DAY 7: Optimization + Report\n🎯 Focus: Improve performance\n🛠 Tasks:\n Analyze:\nOpen rate\nReply rate\nBest subject line\n👉 Optimize:\nRewrite weak email\nImprove CTA\nAdd personalization\n📦 Output:\n ✔ Performance Report\n ✔ Optimization Plan\n\n🎯 FINAL SUBMISSION (7-Day Project)\nIntern must submit:\n✔ 100–200 Leads Sheet\n ✔ 3 Email Templates\n ✔ Campaign Screenshot\n ✔ Metrics:\nOpen rate\nReply rate\n✔ 2 Follow-up Emails\n ✔ Reply Handling Script\n ✔ Results:\nReplies\nInterested leads\nCalls booked (if any)\n\n\n	Interns Project		https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iUYE96f_URz1THe5itYvly03IrQtJ_8jf514Ye6diS8/edit?usp=sharing	8844070f-fcec-4b6e-906c-5d84f1c05f63	2026-05-01 10:53:14.16057	58361633-3c93-4118-940f-9ad9d55f47ea
