28f484a1-5cbf-4816-a01c-269f3c072fa0	Mainnet Deployment(Deploy smart contract on SCAI mainnet network)	Deploy smart contract on SCAI mainnet network\nPrepare documentation & update it in github repository.\nDeploy the project in https://vercel.com/ \nProvide the vercel link when you submit the project.\n	775fa188-9b39-44be-bb77-7238179e139b	\N	completed	medium	\N	\N	intern	775fa188-9b39-44be-bb77-7238179e139b	2026-05-03 13:08:48.922	2026-05-03 13:08:48.922	2026-05-02 06:15:59.65	2026-05-03 13:08:48.922	a9d58204-a99f-4658-915d-26c3d3008e39	1. Pre-Deployment Preparation\nEnvironment Variables: Ensure the production .env is securely populated with the SCAI_MAINNET_RPC_URL and the deployment wallet's PRIVATE_KEY.\n\nGas Funding: Verify the deployer wallet contains a sufficient balance of SCAI tokens to comfortably cover mainnet transaction gas limits.\n\nFinal Audit: Confirm all local Hardhat test suites pass and that the gas optimizations (e.g., custom errors, struct packing) are merged into the main branch.\n\n2. Contract Execution & Verification\nCompile: Run npx hardhat compile to generate the final, clean production ABI.\n\nDeploy: Execute the deployment script targeted specifically at the mainnet:\nnpx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network scai_mainnet\n\nRecord: Immediately document the newly generated mainnet contract address.\n\nVerify: Execute the verification script to publish the source code on the SCAI block explorer, ensuring public transparency:\nnpx hardhat verify --network scai_mainnet <CONTRACT_ADDRESS>\n\n3. Frontend Synchronization\nABI Migration: Move the new production ABI JSON from the Hardhat artifacts folder directly into the frontend repository.\n\nAddress Update: Swap out the testnet/local contract address with the new SCAI mainnet address in the frontend environment configuration (e.g., VITE_MARKETPLACE_ADDRESS).\n\nWagmi Configuration: Update the frontend Wagmi chains array to strictly enforce the SCAI Mainnet and remove any local/testnet fallbacks to prevent accidental misrouting.\n\n4. Immediate Action Items\n[ ] Fund deployer wallet with SCAI.\n\n[ ] Execute deployment and verify the contract.\n\n[ ] Push updated ABI and environment variables to the Vercel production build.\n\n[ ] Perform a live, end-to-end SV-02 minting test on the production frontend to validate the entire pipeline.</CONTRACT_ADDRESS>	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
