51175724-b622-4b60-b0e7-be3a8978161d	da5bdc0e-ba05-4e65-b9d3-a94e96d2e06d	cf89df3e-4b80-41c1-bbdd-fbe3b86a776e	task	2026-05-07 10:33:36.206	2026-05-07 11:22:12.91	48	## objective\n\nThe goal of this project is to build a decentralized token vesting system that allows teams and organizations to distribute tokens securely over time using smart contracts.\n\n## problem statement\n\nMany blockchain projects require structured token distribution for team members, advisors, investors, and contributors. Manual token distribution lacks transparency and increases operational risk. A token vesting system automates this process using programmable smart contracts.\n\n## target users\n\n* Web3 startups\n* DAO organizations\n* Investors and advisors\n* Community contributors\n* Blockchain development teams\n\n## core features\n\n* Create vesting schedules\n* Support cliff periods\n* Linear token unlocking\n* Beneficiary token claiming\n* Admin management controls\n* Vesting dashboard interface\n\n## use cases\n\n* Team token allocation\n* Investor lockup schedules\n* Advisor vesting plans\n* Ecosystem reward distribution\n* Community incentive programs\n\n## technical goals\n\n* Secure smart contract implementation\n* Transparent on-chain transactions\n* Simple frontend interaction\n* Wallet integration support\n* Gas-efficient contract functions\n\n## planned technology stack\n\nFrontend:\n\n* Next.js\n* TailwindCSS\n* Wagmi\n* Viem\n* RainbowKit\n\nBlockchain:\n\n* Solidity\n* OpenZeppelin Contracts\n* Sepolia Testnet\n\nDevelopment Tools:\n\n* Hardhat\n* MetaMask\n* Etherscan	2026-05-07 16:03:36.209093
